reviewText: Worked really well and came fast! I was satisfied with this purchase!

This volume is the best one out there for Dan Doh!
I knocked one star off, because the corner of the dvd case was chipped.
But, the overall quality of the episodes is great. Love the music, and the epic golf story.
I listened to the English dub version, and it was fine. I enjoyed it very much!

Disc 1 episodes:
1. Dan Doh's Dream
2. The Championship
3. Yuka
4. Miss Shot
5. Smiley Ball

Disc 2 episodes:
6. Yokota
7. Final Round
8. Father
9. The 6 Iron
10. Over the Valley
